بِسْمِ اللّٰهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ

This project is dedicated to serving the Holy Quran and making it accessible
to people around the world. May Allah accept this effort and bless all who
contribute to spreading the word of Islam.

وَنُنَزِّلُ مِنَ الْقُرْآنِ مَا هُوَ شِفَاءٌ وَرَحْمَةٌ لِّلْمُؤْمِنِينَ

"And We send down of the Quran that which is healing and mercy for the believers"
- Quran 17:82